{"tid":1954504,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃店Call4van又比死黑警搞","createTime":"2020-04-02T01:16:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T06:40:16.000Z","uid":61766,"like":62,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"3145e03081751a7881127f003f05de40c35d1817","tid":1954504,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T01:16:05.000Z","msg":"明報報道，今日(4月1號)晏晝，「交通部特遣隊」假扮顧客透過CALL4VAN客貨車app電召兩架貨van，<span style=\"color: red;\">及後以「非法駕駛汽車作出租或載客取酬用途」同「駕駛汽車時沒有(附帶載客取酬條款嘅)第三者保險」檢控兩名司機。</span><br />\n<br />\n根據第374章《道路交通條例》：「貨、貨物包括任何類別的負重。」英文為：&ldquo; goods &rdquo; includes burden of any description.<br />\n<br />\n立法會CB(1)1791/13-14(02)號文件亦指出：「...輕型客貨車獲准以出租或取酬的形式載貨，但不能接載攜帶個人財物的乘客。然而，同一條條例亦解釋，個人財物可以是小型私人財物，亦可以是貨或貨物。」<br />\n<br />\n故此，希望各位電召客貨車時，務必遵守相關法例，敬請留意。<br />\n<br />\nSource:  <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/244476908973882/posts/2883172408437639/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F244476908973882%2Fposts%2F2883172408437639%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUt%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=74c0d1b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/244476908973882/posts/2883172408437639/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個極權政府係無停止過清算<br />\n就算有武肺又好 一秒都無停過<br />\n不公不義既畫面每一日係無間斷上眏緊<br />\n<br />\n黃店老闆同員工記得真係要執到正唔好比對家周到<br />\n而手足們 趁呢段時間真係應該好好裝備自己<br />\n你唔揾暴政 暴政會自己搵上門<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb4ebd03ff5304db9218ca076f63810ad91e16f9","tid":1954504,"uid":39710,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T01:18:31.000Z","msg":"香港啲法律又舊又閪"},{"pid":"84e6ae30c28cc9fb59ce53de4391bec83fb6f9dc","tid":1954504,"uid":190333,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T01:21:05.000Z","msg":"姐係當的士坐?"},{"pid":"68c03b6a36aabee5640cb25dc3a4a80fc22151ff","tid":1954504,"uid":63154,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T01:21:41.000Z","msg":"即係個人唔可以跟住啲貨？"},{"pid":"c4042aeb1484b27c0ec500d099293933db2c6c29","tid":1954504,"uid":61766,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb4ebd03ff5304db9218ca076f63810ad91e16f9","tid":1954504,"uid":39710,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T01:18:31.000Z","msg":"香港啲法律又舊又閪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T01:22:31.000Z","msg":"最後淪為打壓反對聲音嘅工具<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac871e323ef186a2e5d4f49f44078146b4603188","tid":1954504,"uid":7125,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T01:24:00.000Z","msg":"之前睇viu tv個戴頭盔 一年已經話最起碼上車前都拎枝水話係貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家咁既時勢比人針就大家要更醒水"},{"pid":"697a5f3c22a812dd98769c1ff264318c9fb0a64f","tid":1954504,"uid":61766,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"84e6ae30c28cc9fb59ce53de4391bec83fb6f9dc","tid":1954504,"uid":190333,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T01:21:05.000Z","msg":"姐係當的士坐?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T01:27:05.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n我自己call的話，有啲司機接單打俾我嘅時候都會問我你係咪真係有貨係身？<br />\n<br />\n今次應該係個司機冇問到啦，跟住黑警放蛇就咁上車亦都冇提及邊一樣係自己嘅貨物.....所以就觸犯左嗰條戇鳩法例"},{"pid":"d228328faaed58a48ffacdb34d73a746cc8a4a89","tid":1954504,"uid":333488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T01:28:08.000Z","msg":"攪左好耐啦， 由於捉uber開始放蛇到而家都差唔多兩年啦， 起碼都拎個紙皮箱當係貨吖，兩手空空就車人，咁的確係柒左少少"},{"pid":"73e74509fb74f15f1b9dbff0caf3e87af8305329","tid":1954504,"uid":51271,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T01:28:41.000Z","msg":"GoGoVan唔會去咬"},{"pid":"ddf76843e5a27b22bf748cb519190c5a904635c9","tid":1954504,"uid":66202,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"697a5f3c22a812dd98769c1ff264318c9fb0a64f","tid":1954504,"uid":61766,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"84e6ae30c28cc9fb59ce53de4391bec83fb6f9dc","tid":1954504,"uid":190333,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20